reviews.text:
🤔🤔🤔 I love ramen and eat alot of it in HK so here's my take on this.
1. Noodles
Ever had Butao in sha tin? Same deal here. Dryer noodles, thin. Even when selecting the firm texture on them still just a bit of a chew and then abundant packaged ramen sensation.  No fault to the chef, its just the noodle. Personally i dont care for these, maybe you do, if so go here. 
2. Meat
Cha siu was .....ok. Def not bad, great flavour, just a bit too much fat for my liking all the while the meat was a bit tuff. Props on the flavor though😎
3. Broth
I got the spicy and thick kind and though it was quite good, it failed to achieve what other places do with the use of extended cooking times. Perhaps this place does cook their broth for 12hrs, i dont actually know, but i do know that its not as good as other places that are similarly priced. It wasnt sweet which is great, savory yes but nothing msg couldnt manage, spicy was good but did lead to a bit of a bitter finish. Id score the broth a 3/5 which for a 85$ bowl of ramen, isnt lovely.
4. Service/Atmosphere
Perfect. Nothing bad at all. Super friendly, prompt to assist. Very good service. 

Overall this is a so so ramen place with great atmosphere and perfect service.
Very delicious Ramen and snacks. Very chewy noodles and good soup base. Worth traveling a long way to Taipo just for a bowl of nice warm Ramen.
Simple menu, good quality, ~$80 per head (lunch)
Medicore food, great music.
Brilliant food, slightly expensive, totally worth it

reviews.text: 價格相宜，吃了味噌拉麵香滑湯底，口味比較淡，幼身拉麵口感很好。免費自家製芽菜辣辣的很惹味開胃。野菜天婦羅外皮薄內裏不乾身。小丸子味道平平。服務員態度很好。可以再encore！

今日過大埔街市買餸，又過嚟和拉麵食碗味增拉麵先☺️ 最鍾意佢呢度啲叉燒，好正好美味！
依家打咭有九折啊！

麵身較幼(似一蘭)，普通湯底較淡但都好味(濃湯要加錢)，自家製免費辣味大荳芽好好味！

成日聽人講：大埔有條隱秘食街，今天一場黎到"和拉麵"就試下佢到底有幾好味喇!~

有豚骨原味、辛辣 同 味增，仲可以叫特濃湯底，點都有款岩你口味；而且可以選擇拉麵既軟硬度，夠哂貼心~!

視覺味覺都好滿足。流心蛋夠哂奪目，叉燒幾肥美，可以俾多塊就好喇

reviews.text:
整體水準都唔錯，算係不過不失
分量都飽 唔使點等
大埔區嚟講拉麵線係食得過
試了黑蒜油豬骨湯拉麵，和煎雞軟骨餃子，都非常好味，會回來再試
拉面沒想像中的濃味，食物還可以，店裏很有日本餐廳的感覺，氣氛很好
經常光顧的一家拉麵 ， 如喜歡拉面朋友可到店一試
湯太小，加湯要$28，又多得濟！
